117
00:28:09,293 --> 00:28:21,939
Thank you for bringing this forward, Prison Affairs, and it's really a wonderful opportunity to say thank you to the youth in our community for taking on this kind of volunteerism.

118
00:28:23,940 --> 00:28:26,921
I love when kids in our city can

119
00:28:29,042 --> 00:28:34,866
